Class CellList

java.lang.Object
CellList
public class CellList
extends java.lang.Object
CellList is a linkedlist specific to holding Cellphones it contains an innerClass CellNode to handle individual nodes of the list serialNum's of CellPhones added to the list must be unique or else it won't be added
Author:
KevinVe

    • getSize

      public int getSize()

    • addToStart

      public void addToStart​(CellPhone cell)
      addToStart method adds a CellPhone to the beginning of the CellList. pushing all other nodes by one iteration. if list already contains the CellPhone's serialNum then it is not added to the list. serialNum must be unique
      Parameters:
      cell - CellPhone to be added to the list

    • insertAtIndex

      public void insertAtIndex​(CellPhone cell, int index)
      insertAtIndex method adds a CellPhone to a specified index. pushing subsequent nodes by one iteration. if list already contains the CellPhone's serialNum then it is not added to the list. serialNum must be unique
      Parameters:
      cell - CellPhone to be added to the list
      index - location in CellList to be inserted at

      public void replaceAtIndex​(CellPhone cell, int index)

      Parameters:

      index - index of CellNode containing the old CellPhone

    • find

      public CellList.CellNode find​(java.lang.Long serial)
      find method searches the CellList for a CellNode that contains a CellPhone with a given serialNum returns first instance of the CellNode as serialNum is assumed to be unique this method causes a privacy leak as this method returns a reference to a node which can be used outside of this class
      Parameters:
      serial - serialNum of CellPhone to be searched for
      Returns:
      CellNode that contains the CellPhone with matching serialNum

    • contains

      public boolean contains​(java.lang.Long serial)
      contains method searches the list for a CellPhone of a given serial number. True if found and false if not.
      Parameters:
      serial - serialNum of CellPhone to be searched for
      Returns:
      if CellList contains cellphone with serial
